            @neumi17 - I guess by "really good players", you mean world-class, and by 4-5 you mean at least 6. Even if you don't like them and you'd like to degrade them, or if you support them and are disappointed that they failed to win 4 matches in a row, think about what words you use and what they mean. Because if a trivial matter such as football makes you lose all capability of rational thought and forget what words mean, that's not good for your health and that's not good for anybody.
